{"tid":84851,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"各區七仔換玻璃樽情況","createTime":"2017-01-18T00:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T21:03:18.000Z","uid":12618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9d60fcf2b253fc27d570b7a908c8565352fb5e","tid":84851,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:19:31.000Z","msg":"七仔今日七點鐘可以換新玻璃樽<br />\n而家八點十分<br />\n我落去樓下換既時候 淨返三個樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換完店員叫我即場check埋 爛左無得退<br />\n當我攞去拆即時候 <br />\n我見到隔離個女人拆緊一箱玻璃樽check緊<br />\n一箱係講緊有三十個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地換左未 有無啲分店已經無貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599ba25f3d1db0c2a3b143dc560d3a8739d5c924","tid":84851,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:20:04.000Z","msg":"換咩玻璃樽 換黎做咩"},{"pid":"980fbdebe9ae68529cf265b05bdc1dd56d04f519","tid":84851,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:21:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換咩玻璃樽 換黎做咩</blockquote><br />\n成日係七仔買野 無特別儲都換到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6386df65b1a64d22a3d721098e1b8ffc67c9f08c","tid":84851,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:26:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>換咩玻璃樽 換黎做咩</blockquote><br />\n成日係七仔買野 無特別儲都換到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩樣的樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全唔知有樽換"},{"pid":"bea4d1e97326ddeec73bd16bc6adbfda6fed389b","tid":84851,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:32:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>換咩玻璃樽 換黎做咩</blockquote><br />\n成日係七仔買野 無特別儲都換到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩樣的樽<img src=\"